{"tid":2215894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財經專題：累積投資近萬億 聘一千萬員工  兩國關係轉壞 日企謀撤出中國","createTime":"2020-09-24T09:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:12:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3266fcb122485005244fd1d967a50a0f02701e2","tid":2215894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/VHTOOT6E3VDMLLDCSXOFEY7TIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FVHTOOT6E3VDMLLDCSXOFEY7TIE%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=ccdcf4b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FVHTOOT6E3VDMLLDCSXOFEY7TIE%2F&h=14cbb3bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/VHTOOT6E3VDMLLDCSXOFEY7TIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n財經專題：累積投資近萬億 聘一千萬員工 <br />\n兩國關係轉壞 日企謀撤出中國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l4Gpg71mA4jR6RnLz1LTBbr_MSU=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUG4URY2FRAM7DNORQ63GUTS2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl4Gpg71mA4jR6RnLz1LTBbr_MSU%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUG4URY2FRAM7DNORQ63GUTS2I.jpg&h=3b431143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■不少日本汽車生產商在中國設廠，倘撤離將令內地失業人數大增。<br />\n<br />\n接替安倍晉三的內閣官房長菅義偉一如所料大熱當選，成日本第99任首相。菅義偉明言在未來外交路線上，會以美日同盟為主軸。現時中美關係惡化，不難估計菅義偉對華政策也可能取決於美國。事實上，安倍晉三仍在任時，美國等西方國家捲起生產基地「去中國化」風潮；日本近月亦推國策引導企業撤華，暫涉資近170.5億元。日本一直是中國低調「金主」，對中國實際投資金額在2018年底已累計至1,119.8億美元（約8,734億港元），冠絕其他國家；在華直接或間接員工逾1,000萬人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東京奧運延期 日本損失2,336億<br />\n<br />\n高調推動「去中國化」的不單止美國，牌面低調的日本同樣不容忽視；。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本擲171億助企業撤離<br />\n<br />\n若單計2018年，實際投資金到位額亦達38億美元，反觀美國在中國外資來源國僅排名第八，其2018年間對中國實際投資金到位額為26.9億美元，比日本少逾四成一。而日企在華直接或間接員工人數超過1,000萬人，換言之，若日企撤資規模達整體一成，已牽涉達百億美元計資金及以百萬計的就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n本報統計10間日本大型企業在中國聘請員工數目，主要為汽車生產商，。。。。。。。。。，主要分佈在日本中小企業，涉及製造業、農林牧漁和建築業等。<br />\n<br />\n日本與中國地理位置鄰近，兩地民眾經濟往來淵源久遠。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n日本前首相安倍晉三及他背後的執政自民黨，近年亦沿着親中國的風向走，原邀請中共總書記習近平今年4月到訪日本；然而，武漢肺炎疫情成為轉捩點，令兩國決定押後有關訪問。後來疫情擴散至全球，日本亦跟隨國際風向，嘗試將廠房生產線搬離中國。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月，日本政府公佈將撥款22億美元（約170.5億港元），協助日本製造商將生產線搬離中國，或轉移至其他國家，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國對中國採取強硬外交模式，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：令內地失業人數增加<br />\n<br />\n冠域商業及經濟研究中心主任關焯照表示，不少日本企業均視中國為生產基地，包括電子產品及車廠等，將不利中國經濟，「撤離導致投資減少、影響經濟活動，最大問題係令內地失業人數增加，加重就業壓力，中國就業市場將持續轉壞」。<br />\n<br />\n關焯照指出，中國生產成本、人工近年已變得不便宜，加上日本親美國，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關焯照又指出，日本企業撤離內地後，沒有其他國家的企業能取代，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7nsOEXcqqOYY167icKPA2dVpels=/596x332/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55KQGH44LJE4VM72ZVNU7W6HHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7nsOEXcqqOYY167icKPA2dVpels%3D%2F596x332%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55KQGH44LJE4VM72ZVNU7W6HHI.gif&h=82d447e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wD8WrEXqPsYqr3NeEdB60fIBnWQ=/596x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZVVGEW6NG5FOTLF3JMAU7AA5DM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwD8WrEXqPsYqr3NeEdB60fIBnWQ%3D%2F596x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZVVGEW6NG5FOTLF3JMAU7AA5DM.gif&h=1484d218&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c955a4ab46aff2589cffab5686ca8a26a132764","tid":2215894,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28743c98d77777dc52b27bb6ce084700366307f4","tid":2215894,"uid":159583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:35.000Z","msg":"要不是日本  中國早就完蛋了"},{"pid":"6646cb30b754a82ddbbcce8a038eee8e1e47bd5d","tid":2215894,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"叫支那賠返個奧運嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d013eebf62c28f1f79443d6b8b6732e819e2ca7","tid":2215894,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"企/攤+10,000,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fff33c575bc5fbec142822db7ddd47aa75c252","tid":2215894,"uid":39320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6646cb30b754a82ddbbcce8a038eee8e1e47bd5d","tid":2215894,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"叫支那賠返個奧運嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"南京事件仲未同你計 (其實一直都有俾錢支那）"}]}